#: ../../../autoapi/tilelang/language/builtin/index.rst:349
msgid ""
"Emits `tl::get_warp_idx_sync(warp_size)` which divides the block-linear "
"thread id by `warp_size`, matching the semantics of CUTLASS' canonical "
"helpers."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../autoapi/tilelang/language/builtin/index.rst:367
msgid ""
"Lowers to `tl::get_warp_idx(warp_size)` which divides the block-linear "
"thread id by the provided `warp_size` without requiring warp convergence."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../autoapi/tilelang/language/builtin/index.rst:375
